    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 5.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "事務所のみんなから、凄い勢いでメッセが来てる\nなになに……「琴乃と何があったの」「最低です」",
      "startTime": 5.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "「ポンコツ男が修羅場とか、ザマァ」……だと……？\nお……俺、琴乃に一体何をしたんだ……！？",
      "startTime": 15.1333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 13633.333333400002,
          "startTime": 28.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12859.6594175,
          "startTime": 27.9929927508
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 20.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 20.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　みんなからいっせいにメッセがきて\n全員、なぜか{user}さんに怒ってる？",
      "startTime": 25.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 28.3596594174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "……ほんとだ。なぜか『{user}さんが\n私を弄んで捨てた』ってことになってますね",
      "startTime": 32.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんにも「琴乃ちゃんは麻奈ちゃんの大事な妹よ」\nって泣かれてるんだが、意味が分からないんだ……",
      "startTime": 41.1710652033,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 44.904399681
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、私にもなんでこうなったのかは全然……\n…………あ！！",
      "startTime": 50.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 51.7666209537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、私にお好み焼きを奢ってくれた後\n「琴乃に大事な用がある」って言ってたじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 55.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "でもその後、その話をする暇が全然なかったので\nかわりに聞いてもらえないかって、渚に相談しました",
      "startTime": 63.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 67.2863029478
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら、渚が他の子に話すうちに尾ひれが付いて\n{user}さんが駄目男になったのかも……",
      "startTime": 72.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 76.2095679598
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの中での俺のイメージって一体……\nでも俺、大事な用がある、なんて言ったっけ？",
      "startTime": 79.8670678692,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "言ってましたよ！\nその直後に、鞄を取りに戻っちゃいましたけど",
      "startTime": 86.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 90.4524246849
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "公演初日……鞄…………思い出した！！\n待っててくれ、今ちょっと取ってくるから！",
      "startTime": 96.5857568738,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3347.5739165000105,
          "startTime": 99.9333307903
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4914.240583100011,
          "startTime": 101.4999974569
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 99.2857554751
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "取ってくるって、何をですか？\n……あ、行っちゃった",
      "startTime": 102.3999974569,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3500,
          "startTime": 105.8999974569
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2333.333333400006,
          "startTime": 104.7333307903
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 105.5663446106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、もう帰ってきた\nあの、そのプレゼントの包みみたいなのは？",
      "startTime": 109.0999974569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3733738896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、琴乃にこれを渡すつもりだったんだよ",
      "startTime": 113.3733738896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタインにもらったチョコのお返しなんだが\nすっかり遅くなってしまったな、悪い",
      "startTime": 120.5067060785,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5796.020624799993,
          "startTime": 123.3693945144
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4933.3333334,
          "startTime": 125.4400394119
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 123.9067072229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……あ、ありがとうございます\n美味しそうなキャラメルの詰め合わせですね",
      "startTime": 129.9666641236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、その………………これだけ？",
      "startTime": 133.2967118895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 139.0126528735
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、お礼をもらえるのはもちろん嬉しいんです\nでも、凄く大事なことみたいに言ってたので",
      "startTime": 143.2509212922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "わざわざ琴乃がバレンタインチョコをくれたんだから\nそのお返しは、大事なことだろう",
      "startTime": 150.0226833021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 152.6226844465
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "あれは本当に、ただのお礼だったんですから\nそんなに重く捉えないで下さい！",
      "startTime": 155.9172875218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがあんな風に言うものだから\n私、てっきり……",
      "startTime": 161.6666641236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "てっきり？",
      "startTime": 163.750351937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 165.0836852704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもありません！！\nふふっ……でも、そうでした",
      "startTime": 168.1333307903,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 172.7357710832
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんもだいぶ面倒くさかったですけど\n{user}さんも大概、鈍い人でしたね",
      "startTime": 176.4230552593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "え？\n俺って今、そんな呆れられるようなこと言ったか？",
      "startTime": 181.3991873417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 185.5658551527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_13_03-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、莉央さん達にはこの後謝っておきます\nサプライズゲストの件で打ち合わせもあるので",
      "startTime": 189.6999974569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
